      <h2>Engine Warranty Coverage</h2>
      <p>
        At <strong>AutoBids</strong>, we stand behind every engine sold through our platform. Our warranty program is designed to give you peace of mind — whether you're buying for a daily driver, project car, or commercial fleet.
      </p>

      <h3>Standard Warranty (Included)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Coverage:</strong> 3 months or 5,000 km (whichever comes first) from the date of delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Applies to:</strong> Engine long block only — block, head(s), pistons, crankshaft, camshaft, timing gears, and valves.</li>
        <li><strong>Excludes:</strong> All bolt-on components (e.g., alternator, turbo, starter, injectors, wiring, sensors, intake/exhaust manifolds).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Optional Extended Warranty</h3>
      <p>
        Customers can upgrade to 6- or 12-month warranties for select engines. Coverage options include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Parts & labor reimbursement (up to $500–$1,000 depending on tier)</li>
        <li>In-shop diagnostic support</li>
        <li>Shipping protection for return claims</li>
      </ul>
      <p><em>Extended warranties must be purchased at checkout and cannot be added after delivery.</em></p>

      <h3>Eligibility & Conditions</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>All installations must be performed by a certified mechanic or repair facility.</li>
        <li>Engines must be installed within 15 days of delivery.</li>
        <li>All fluids, gaskets, filters, and belts must be replaced at time of installation.</li>
        <li>Proof of professional installation and service records may be required for warranty claims.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>What’s Not Covered</h3>
      <p>
        Our warranty does <strong>not</strong> cover:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Damage due to overheating, insufficient lubrication, abuse, or neglect</li>
        <li>Improper installation or failure to replace required maintenance components</li>
        <li>Performance modifications or use in racing/off-road applications</li>
        <li>Labor or towing unless otherwise stated in your extended plan</li>
      </ul>

